description: Baseline traffic situation of driving with ego vehicle as AV
The ego car is overtaken by the target car from the inside
The target car tailgates the ego car
The target car brakes abruptly to avoid collision
The target car brakes abruptly
The target car starts late when traffic lights turn green
The target car starts late when traffic lights turn green with a pedestrian
The target car cuts off from the right lane
The target car is zigzagging
The target car flashes lights to the ego car
The ego car’s changing lane is prevented by a platoon of AVs
The target car drives slowly in front of the ego car
The target car changes lanes to let the ego car behind overtake
The target car attempts to move from the centre to the left lane but goes back to the centre lane so as not to block an ego car behind
The platoon of AVs lower the speed to let the ego car change lane
The target car is waiting for pedestrians to cross the road
the target car follows its front car with a too large gap
The target car passes the intersection exactly at the time when the light changes without deceleration
The target car plans to overtake but canceled the process and move back
The target car obeys the speed limit when the traffic flow drive at around 70
The target car brakes abruptly to avoid collision with a pedestrian
